'''Carlos Meglia''' was an [[Wikipedia:Argentina|Argentinian]] artist who did the pencils and inking for ''[[Underworld: The Yavin Vassilika]]'' and "[[Lando's Commandos: On Eagles' Wings]]." He died at the age of fifty in [[August]] [[2008]].
